title: Turbo Dismount v1.11.2
description:
Turbo Dismount 1.11 "Grim Season" Update!

The weather has been grim in Finland, so this is a grim season update.

    New vehicle: "Grim Wagon"
    New seasonal head for grim season, the Grim Visage
    New camera mode, the Cinematic Camera!
    Better touch screen support for Windows tablets
    Shuriken tweaked, vehicle logo fixed
    Cop cars tweaked 


Enjoy this grim, grim update in quiet solemnity.

*Update 1.11.1 fixes game launch freeze on older operating systems*
*Update 1.11.2 fixes Workshop connectivity on older operating systems*
